# Deep Research Enterprise Configuration

## Required Environment Variables

### API Keys (Required)
```bash
# Together.ai API Key - Get from https://api.together.xyz/
TOGETHER_API_KEY=your_together_api_key_here

# Exa Search API Key - Get from https://exa.ai/
EXA_API_KEY=your_exa_api_key_here
```

### Application Configuration (Optional)
```bash
# Node environment: development, staging, production
NODE_ENV=development

# Server configuration (if using HTTP server)
PORT=3000
HOST=0.0.0.0

# Logging configuration
LOG_LEVEL=info
# Options: debug, info, success, warn, error
LOG_FORMAT=json
# Options: json, pretty

# Enable colors in logs (true/false)
LOG_COLORS=true
```

### Research Configuration (Optional)
```bash
# Maximum number of search queries per research cycle
MAX_QUERIES=2

# Maximum number of sources to include in final synthesis
MAX_SOURCES=5

# Maximum number of tokens in generated report
MAX_COMPLETION_TOKENS=8192

# Number of research refinement cycles
RESEARCH_BUDGET=2
```

### Performance & Scalability (Optional)
```bash
# Redis connection for caching (if enabled)
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# PostgreSQL connection for persistence (if enabled)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/deepresearch

# Request timeout in milliseconds
REQUEST_TIMEOUT=300000

# Maximum concurrent requests
MAX_CONCURRENT_REQUESTS=10
```

### Monitoring & Telemetry (Optional)
```bash
# Enable Prometheus metrics endpoint
ENABLE_METRICS=true

# Metrics port (default: same as PORT)
METRICS_PORT=9090

# Enable OpenTelemetry tracing
ENABLE_TRACING=false

# Jaeger endpoint for traces
JAEGER_ENDPOINT=http://localhost:14268/api/traces
```

### Security (Optional)
```bash
# Enable rate limiting
ENABLE_RATE_LIMIT=true

# Rate limit: requests per minute per IP
RATE_LIMIT_RPM=60

# Enable prompt injection detection
ENABLE_PROMPT_INJECTION_DETECTION=true

# Sanitize error messages in production
SANITIZE_ERRORS=true
```

### Cost Management (Optional)
```bash
# Enable cost tracking
ENABLE_COST_TRACKING=true

# Cost budget per request in USD
MAX_COST_PER_REQUEST=1.00

# Alert when cost threshold reached (percentage)
COST_ALERT_THRESHOLD=80
```

## Setup Instructions

1. Copy this file to `.env`:
   ```bash
   cp .env.example .env
   ```

2. Fill in your API keys:
   - Get Together.ai API key from: https://api.together.xyz/
   - Get Exa API key from: https://exa.ai/

3. Adjust optional settings as needed for your environment

4. Never commit `.env` file to version control!

## Environment-Specific Configurations

### Development
```bash
NODE_ENV=development
LOG_LEVEL=debug
LOG_COLORS=true
SANITIZE_ERRORS=false
```

### Staging
```bash
NODE_ENV=staging
LOG_LEVEL=info
SANITIZE_ERRORS=true
ENABLE_METRICS=true
```

### Production
```bash
NODE_ENV=production
LOG_LEVEL=warn
SANITIZE_ERRORS=true
ENABLE_METRICS=true
ENABLE_RATE_LIMIT=true
ENABLE_COST_TRACKING=true
```

## Validation

The application will validate all required environment variables on startup.
Missing required variables will cause the application to exit with a clear error message.
